description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare Naked Ghosts, Zombie Roads & Prison Poltergeists Edition

Dave & Tim share some fascinating listener emails and encounters with the supernatural and take a long, hard look at the strange week that was. Haunted Prison Ghosts, Creepy Colorado locations, naked ghosts, Zombie roads and so much more, PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind.

Get your hands on Dave's Package Here: www.darknessradio.com/store
